sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as PaymentController
    participant S as PaymentService
    participant B as BillRepository
    participant DB as Database

    U->>C: Payment request
    C->>S: process payment

    S->>B: fetch bill
    S->>S: validate amount

    S->>DB: insert payment
    S->>DB: update bill (paid/partial)

    DB-->>U: confirmation